headline: Better Fintech Stock: Block vs. PayPal
summary: One of the most important trends that has shaped the economy during the past decade has happened at the intersection of financial services and technology.  Two companies, Block (NYSE: XYZ) and PayPal (NASDAQ: PYPL), are among those enterprises leading the charge.  Shares of these businesses haven't quite panned out for investors.
